Saboda yawan girgizar ƙasa da ke faruwa a ƙasar Indonesia, ƙasar ba ta shirya ba don fushin yanayi.
Ko da yake an gina gine-ginen tsunami a Ače, ba a yawan yin su a wasu wurare ba.
Saboda rashin sautin da ake kira tsunami, babu shakka, mutuwar da aka yi a birnin Bulus ta ƙaru sosai.
Yin tafiya a tsakanin tsibiran Indonesiya yana da wuya a lokacin da ya fi dacewa.
Bala'i na zahiri yana ƙara rikitarwa ga kayan aiki.
Jirgin asibiti da ke kula da waɗanda suka ji rauni a girgizar ƙasa da ke Lomboke yana zuwa Palau amma zai isa wurin da ya faru a cikin kwanaki uku.
Shugaban kasar Joko Widodo ya zaɓi sake gina kayayyakin more rayuwa a Indonesia da aka rushe a matsayin cibiyar yakin neman zabensa, ya ba da gudummawar kuɗi ga hanyoyi da jiragen kasa.
Amma rashin kudaden bai ba gwamnatin Joko kwanciyar hankali ba, domin zai sake yin zabe a shekara mai zuwa.
Hakazalika, ana matsa lamba a kan Yoko saboda tashin hankali na addinai a Indonesia, inda yawancin Musulmai ke bin addinin addini mai tsaron gida.
