Amma a ranar Alhamis, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya ce a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa, 'Tallafin da Majalisar ta dauka dole ne a ci gaba da tsaurara ba tare da wani fansa ba har sai an kammala cikakken kawar da makaman nukiliya da aka tabbatar da hujja.
Majalisar tsaron ta amince da takunkumi da aka yi wa Koriya ta Arewa tun shekara ta 2006 don hana ta samun kuɗin shiga a cikin shirin nukiliya da makaman nukiliya na ballistic.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a bayan taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kuma daga bisani ya ce zai sake ziyarci Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya wani taro.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma ba a yi nasara ba a ziyarar da ya gabata.
Ya bar birnin Pyongyang a watan Yuli, yana cewa, duk ci gaban da aka samu na nufin cewa, bayan sa'o'i kadan, Koriya ta Arewa za ta sanar da cewa ta yi amfani da 'yan bindigar 'yan gangster.
