A cikin shekara ta 2014, an shirya sabon jirgin ruwan soja na Jamus don maye gurbin jiragen ruwan Cold War, amma a cewar kafofin yada labarai na gida, ba za mu ga shi ba har zuwa shekara ta gaba saboda tsarin da ke ci gaba da aiki da kuma tsadar farashi.
A cewar wani wakilin rundunar sojin, wanda jaridar Die Zeit ta ruwaito, an dage aikin shigar da manyan jiragen ruwa na jirgin ruwan na Baden-Wuerttemberg zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019.
