A cikin sabon rahoton Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Yanayi ta Florida (FWC), an ce yawan ambaliyar Redwood yana raguwa a cikin akwatin kifaye na Tampa Bay.
FWC ta ce an samu karin ci gaban a cikin lardunan Paineal, Manaci, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, wanda ya nuna cewa taro ya ragu.
Ruwan ya yi ta hurawa a kusan mil 130 na gabar teku daga arewacin Painelas zuwa kudancin lardin Li.
